  • highlight.js v11.9.0 — BSD-3-Clause License
    Copyright (c) 2006, Ivan Sagalaev and other contributors
    https://github.com/highlightjs/highlight.js/blob/main/LICENSE

  • js-beautify v1.15.1 — MIT License
