    https://github.com/beautifier/js-beautify/blob/main/LICENSE

Their license banners are retained inline where each library is embedded.

The HTML file-type icon (favicon and header icon) is from vscode-icons,
MIT License, Copyright (c) 2016 Roberto Huertas and contributors
(https://github.com/vscode-icons/vscode-icons/blob/master/LICENSE).
